[center][img]http://i1136.photobucket.com/albums/n490/guner123/darkclawz.png[/img][/center] Hello guys i am working on a new base the base i used was a[u][size=12pt] blank pi[/size][/u] i am working on this by my self at the moment but i hope for people to apply if know one apply's then this base will take me a long time do get done i hope to turn this blank pi into a server that is good enough to host.
I know 634 items are not special but don't moan about it please thank you
[b]development team source sided: liamp(me)[/b]
[code]stuff that has been added 634 item has been added by a mate nex boss with animations by a mate woodcutting about 90-95% done has stumps fixed some items that where in wrong slots ( there are still loads to fix :/ ) added darkclawz v3 instead of report abuse changed from darkclawz v3 to darkclawz rules added a interface to the rule book <3 when click i disagree in the interface it disconnects you from the game New hit plates added New hp bar's are added fix fire cape now its the real rs one [/code]
[size=12pt][size=14pt]few pictures new pictures [/size][/size][img]http://i1136.photobucket.com/albums/n490/guner123/rspsloveu.png[/img] [img]http://i1136.photobucket.com/albums/n490/guner123/SSScreenCapture108-1.png[/img] [img]http://i1136.photobucket.com/albums/n490/guner123/SSScreenCapture119.png[/img] [img]http://i1136.photobucket.com/albums/n490/guner123/SSScreenCapture102.png[/img] named from darkclawz v3 to darkclawz rules [img]http://i1136.photobucket.com/albums/n490/guner123/rulesinterface.png[/img] [size=12pt][size=14pt]older pictures[/size][/size] [img]http://i1136.photobucket.com/albums/n490/guner123/SSScreenCapture017-1.png[/img] [img]http://i1136.photobucket.com/albums/n490/guner123/SSScreenCapture020.png[/img] [img]http://i1136.photobucket.com/albums/n490/guner123/SSScreenCapture021-1.png[/img] [img]http://i1136.photobucket.com/albums/n490/guner123/SSScreenCapture022.png[/img]
i know this is not that much to look at but i am working on my own and this will take some time to get done unless people apply don't moan about there is not much content i know but i am starting blank and i am trying to add content :D
[b]apply what i need is another source programmer and a client please apply[/b] [code] name: age: contact details msn or skype: if you rated your self what would you give your self out of 10: proof of work?: [/code]
